name: Does This Shirt Make My Bass Look Big! Tshirt
description: This is a funny shirt to make any fishing trip enjoyable.  Put this on and a bad day will soon be fun.  Shirts are made by Gildan and are 100% cotton.  We can make them in any size or color you want.  Just let us know what you want.  We aim to please.

name: JT Jigs
description: JT Jigs are made with quality in mind.  If they didn't catch kicker bass we wouldn't make them.  Slowly bounce them off the bottom or pull them over a rocky point and set the hook when you feel that sweet tug at the end of your line.  JT Jigs will get those Big O Bucket Heads to bite!

name: Hogzillia Worms!
description: These are true fish catching 10 inch worms!  If you are a tournament angler or looking to catch a trophy bass tie one of these on and you'll be saying EHH!!!  Hogzillia!
